These makefiles aims to compile bootloader + slots which contain firmware

Here are the makefiles needed :

bootonslot.mk   =>  Entry points of the following Makefiles. This makefiles must be include in $(RIOTBASE)/Makefile.include
variables.mk    =>  Variables needed by the following Makefiles :
bootloader.mk   =>  To compile the bootloader
multislot.mk    =>  To compile a bootloader + 2 slots
singleslot.mk   =>  To compile a bootloader + 1 slots

